{"id":29747757702,"name":"Test","node_id":"WFR_kwLOA_1uaM8AAAAG7RrChg","head_branch":"fix-jpacriteria-store-map-race","head_sha":"f8506156761e69f624657f06b86b44fc837d8f1b","path":".github/workflows/run-tests.yml","run_number":54878,"run_attempt":1,"event":"pull_request","display_title":"fix: thread-safe store-map init in JpaCriteriaQueryEngine","status":"completed","conclusion":"success","workflow_id":10954,"check_suite_id":80552642186,"check_suite_node_id":"CS_kwDOA_1uaM8AAAASwU_Gig","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/29747757702","html_url":"https://github.com/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/29747757702","pull_requests":[{"id":4091578265,"number":24508,"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/pulls/24508","head":{"ref":"fix-jpacriteria-store-map-race","sha":"f8506156761e69f624657f06b86b44fc837d8f1b","repo":{"id":66940520,"name":"dhis2-core","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core"}},"base":{"ref":"master","sha":"9a14735772b8d56cd5048f53150e811b4663c04d","repo":{"id":66940520,"name":"dhis2-core","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core"}}}],"created_at":"2026-07-20T13:47:20Z","updated_at":"2026-07-20T13:55:15Z","run_started_at":"2026-07-20T13:47:20Z","jobs_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/29747757702/jobs","logs_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/29747757702/logs","check_suite_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/check-suites/80552642186","artifacts_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/29747757702/artifacts","cancel_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/29747757702/cancel","rerun_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/29747757702/rerun","head_commit":{"message":"fix: thread-safe store-map init in JpaCriteriaQueryEngine\n\nJpaCriteriaQueryEngine resolved its per-entity store lookup lazily on the\nfirst query(), via an unsynchronized check-then-act over a plain HashMap:\n\n    if (!stores.isEmpty()) return;\n    for (store : hibernateGenericStores) stores.put(store.getClazz(), store);\n\nWhen several threads make the very first metadata query concurrently (e.g.\nparallel tracker imports against a freshly-started instance), they populate\nthe shared HashMap at the same time. The concurrent puts can corrupt the map\n(lost/unreachable entries during resize), after which getStore() returns null\nfor an entity class that is actually registered. query() then short-circuits:\n\n    if (store == null) return new ArrayList\u003c\u003e();\n\ni.e. it returns an empty result WITHOUT querying the database. In the tracker\nimporter this makes preheat fail to resolve existing metadata (Program,\nOrganisationUnit, DataElement, ... - whichever class loses the race), so every\nimport fails validation with 409 CONFLICT for the whole lifetime of that\ninstance. The failure is intermittent and independent of the code under test,\nwhich is why it has hit both baseline and candidate in the performance-compare\njob.\n\nFix: populate the store map once, eagerly, in a @PostConstruct method (runs\nsingle-threaded as part of the Spring lifecycle) and drop the lazy init from\ngetStore(); concurrent callers now only ever read a fully-populated map. The\nmap is also switched to ConcurrentHashMap as defence in depth.\n\nThe defect has existed since the lazy init was introduced (2023); it was\nexposed recently by the concurrent tracker-import performance workload.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.8 (1M context) \u003cnoreply@anthropic.com\u003e","author":{"name":"Enrico","email":"enrico@dhis2.org"},"id":"f8506156761e69f624657f06b86b44fc837d8f1b","tree_id":"8f1f8b2934e243ad838ae20b34f7317f3d9255d8","timestamp":"2026-07-20T13:43:58Z","committer":{"name":"Enrico","email":"enrico@dhis2.org"}},"workflow_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/workflows/10954","repository":{"id":66940520,"node_id":"MDEwOlJlcG9zaXRvcnk2Njk0MDUyMA==","owner":{"login":"dhis2","id":1089987,"node_id":"MDEyOk9yZ2FuaXphdGlvbjEwODk5ODc=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1089987?v=4","html_url":"https://github.com/dhis2","gravatar_id":"","type":"Organization","site_admin":false,"url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/events{/privacy}","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/following{/other_user}","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/followers","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/gists{/gist_id}","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/orgs","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/received_events","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/repos","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/subscriptions"},"name":"dhis2-core","full_name":"dhis2/dhis2-core","description":"DHIS 2 Core. Written in Java. Contains the service layer and Web API.","html_url":"https://github.com/dhis2/dhis2-core","fork":false,"private":false,"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core","archive_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/{archive_format}{/ref}","assignees_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/assignees{/user}","blobs_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/git/blobs{/sha}","branches_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/branches{/branch}","collaborators_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/collaborators{/collaborator}","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/comments{/number}","commits_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/commits{/sha}","compare_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/compare/{base}...{head}","contents_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/contents/{+path}","contributors_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/contributors","dep